Jonathan Goldstein (actor) https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Jonathan_Goldstein_(actor) 0 Jonathan Goldstein (born December 4, 1964) is an American actor, director and musician best known for his role as Walter Nichols in the Nickelodeon sitcom Drake Josh (2004–2007).
